text: Fire Chief is a 1940 Disney cartoon. It stars Donald Duck and his nephews Huey, Dewey, and Louie. ==Voice cast== * Clarence Nash as Donald Duck and Huey, Dewey, and Louie ==Home media== The short was released on May 18, 2004, on Walt Disney Treasures: The Chronological Donald, Volume One: 1934-1941. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:Disney animated movies Category:Donald Duck Category:Short movies
title: Fire Chief (movie)
